        <updateDate>2023-08-02T19:55:21Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Guard, Reserve, and Active Duty Department of Veterans Affairs Educational Assistance Parity Act of 2021 or the GRAD VA Educational Assistance Parity Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill expands eligibility for Post-9/11 educational assistance to members of the National Guard who perform full-time National Guard duty or full-time service in the National Guard when performing active duty.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
